      "next": "A1_LOW_DEEP_Q"
    },
    {
      "id": "A1_LOW_DEEP_Q",
      "type": "question",
      "text": "What made it harder to act in that moment?",
      "options": [
        "I kept second-guessing myself",
        "I was waiting for someone else to step in",
        "I felt overwhelmed by everything happening",
        "I didn’t know what the right move was"
